Message Format:
+---------------+-------+-------+---------------+---------------+-------------------------------
|    LEN(2)     |Type(1)|Err(1) |    SID(2)     |    Seq(2)     |    Param Buffer(n)
+---------------+-------+-------+---------------+---------------+-------------------------------
Type: 0-Req, 1-Resp

Param Buffer Format:
+---------------+---------------+--------------
|   Type(2)     |   Length(2)   |   Data(m)
+---------------+-------+-------+--------------
Type: INTEGER/BUF
